     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <pb facs="4"/>
   <head>To <hi>Ouerburies</hi> Widow, wife of <hi>this Husband.</hi>
   </head>
   <lg>
      <l>LEaue worthy Wife to weare your mourning weed,</l>
      <l>Or bootlesse staine your che<gap reason="illegible" resp="#apex" extent="1+ letters">
            <desc>•…</desc>
         </gap>ks for him thats dead;</l>
      <l>But rather ioy, and thanke this Authors pen,</l>
      <l>Hath so well match'd thee with this matchlesse man:</l>
      <l>For <hi>Ouerburies</hi> Ghost is glad to see,</l>
      <l>His widow such one's happy wife to be.</l>
   </lg>
   <p>
      <hi>R. S.</hi>
   </p>
</div>
